《'''Where the Dream Takes You'''》是一首由美國歌手[[Mýa|Mýa]]錄製與演唱的一首情歌。該歌曲由[[詹姆斯·紐頓·霍華|James Netwon Howard]]與[[Diane_Warren|Diane Warren]]共同創作<ref>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=CRQEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA20&lpg=PA20&dq=Mya+where+the+dream+takes+you+billboard&source=bl&ots=2BhxszOJPT&sig=P8zDGs0rxkj6IbllLGg22tg7P_k&hl=en&ei=-2KyTfWxKafw0gHN8rWMBQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=4&ved=0CCkQ6AEwAw#v=onepage&q=Mya%20where%20the%20dream%20takes%20you%20billboard&f=false|title=Soundtracks and Film Score News|accessdate=2011-04-23|work=[[Google_Books|Google Books]]}}</ref>。該歌曲以[[宣传单曲|宣傳單曲]]的形式於2001年6月5日於[[當代流行電台|當代流行電台]]與[[成人當代電台|成人當代電台]]發表<ref name="Disney2">{{cite web|url=http://www.thefreelibrary.com/A%26M%2FInterscope+Recording+Artist+Mya+Records+%60%60Where+the+Dream+Takes...-a074690656|title=A&M/Interscope Recording Artist Mya Records ``Where the Dream Takes You'' for ``Atlantis: The Lost Empire'' Soundtrack On Walt Disney Records|accessdate=2016-05-24|work=[[The_Free_Library|The Free Library]]|archive-date=2016-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160623212506/http://www.thefreelibrary.com/A%26M%2FInterscope+Recording+Artist+Mya+Records+%60%60Where+the+Dream+Takes...-a074690656|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

